- Anthocyanins are extracted for 30 minutes (under agitation. Keep in the dark) from petals using MeOH containing HCl 0.05% v/v. 
            You can put the tissue in a 50 mL tube for this and cover it with aluminium foil.
- The anthocyanins were dried in a speedvac at room temperature. 
- Dry anthocyanins can be stored at -20ÂºC

